a]]|ESA}} || 6.46m\n|{{flagathlete|[[Ramiro Sandoval]]|NCA}} || 6.37m\n|-\n|[[Triple Jump]]\n|{{flagathlete|[[Kessel Campbell]]|HON}} || 15.06m '''[[List of Central American Junior and Youth Championships records#Boys .28U-20.29|CR]]'''\n|{{flagathlete|[[Marvin Garc\u00eda]]|GUA}} || 14.93m\n|{{flagathlete|[[Josell Ram\u00edrez]]|CRC}} || 14.34m\n|-\n|[[Shot Put]]\n|{{flagathlete|[[Luis Folgar]]|GUA}} || 13.37m '''[[List of Central American Junior and Youth Championships records#Boys .28U-20.29|CR]]'''\n|{{flagathlete|[[Juan De Le\u00f3n]]|ESA}} || 13.33m\n|{{flagathlete|[[Emanuel \u00c1lvarez]]|CRC}} || 13.03m\n|-\n|[[Discus Throw]]\n|{{flagathlete|[[Emanuel \u00c1lvarez]]|CRC}} || 42.68m '''[[List of Central American Junior and Youth Championships records#Boys .28U-20.29|CR]]'''\n|{{flagathlete|[[Jos\u00e9 Barcos]]|GUA}} || 39.82m\n|{{flagathlete|[[Atila Pastora]]|NCA}} || 38.52m\n|-\n|[[Hammer Throw]]\n|{{flagathlete|[[Jos\u00e9 Barcos]]|GUA}} || 51.11m '''[[List of Central American Junior and Youth Championships records#Boys .28U-20.29|CR]]'''\n|{{flagathlete|[[Edgar Flori\u00e1n]]|GUA}} || 47.95m\n|{{flagathlete|[[Jairo Alvarado]]|CRC}} || 44.59m\n|-\n|[[Javelin Throw]]\n|{{flagathlete|[[Adri\u00e1n Zepeda]]|NCA}} || 56.75m\n|{{flagathlete|[[Elder Contreras]]|GUA}} || 48.46m\n|{{flagathlete|[[Jonathan G\u00f3mez (athlete)|Jonathan G\u00f3mez]]|CRC}} || 46.41m\n|-\n|[[Decathlon]]\n|{{flagathlete|[[Darvin Col\u00f3n]]|HON}} || 6121 '''[[List of Central American Junior and Youth Championships records#Boys .28U-20.2|CR]]'''\n|{{flagathlete|[[Edwin Campos]]|CRC}} || 5392\n|{{flagathlete|[[Alex Evans (athlete)|Alex Evans]]|BIZ}} || 3561\n|-\n|[[Racewalking|10,000 metres Walk]]\n|{{flagathlete|[[V\u00edctor Hugo Mendoza]]|ESA}} || 44:37.78 '''[[List of Central American Junior and Youth Championships records#Boys .28U-20.29|CR]]'''\n|{{flagathlete|[[Yassir Cabrera]]|PAN}} || 45:00.00\n|{{flagathlete|[[Jos\u00e9 Guzm\u00e1n (athlete)|Jos\u00e9 Guzm\u00e1n]]|ESA}} || 48: